title: $:/plugins/joshuafontany/tw5-yjs/CreateWikiFromEdition/SetListedEditions

\define thisPrefix() [[

\define thisSuffix() ]]

Editions listed here will appear in the drop-down menu for creating new
wikis from editions. If no editions are listed here than all available editions
will be listed for creating new wikis.

Add Edition To List:
<$select
  tiddler='$:/state/tw5-yjs/AddEditionToList'
>
  <option value=''>
    Select Edition
  </option>
  <$list
    filter='[[$:/state/tw5-yjs/AvailableEditionList]indexes[]search{$:/state/tw5-yjs/AddEditionToList!!search}] -[enlist{$:/ListedEditions!!text}]'
  >
    <$set
      name=Annoying
      filter='[<currentTiddler>]'
      emptyValue=<<currentTiddler>>
    >
      <option
        value=<<Annoying>>
      >
        <<currentTiddler>>
      </option>
    </$set>
  </$list>
</$select>
<$button>
  Add
  <$action-listops
    $tiddler='$:/ListedEditions'
    $field='text'
    $subfilter='+[append{$:/state/tw5-yjs/AddEditionToList}]'
  />
</$button>
Narrow List:
<$edit-text
  tiddler='$:/state/tw5-yjs/AddEditionToList'
  field='search'
/>

Currently Listed (uncheck to remove from list):

<$list
  filter='[enlist{$:/ListedEditions!!text}]'
>
  <$button
    class='tc-btn-invisible'
  >
    <$list
      filter='[enlist{$:/ListedEditions!!text}title<currentTiddler>addprefix<thisPrefix>addsuffix<thisSuffix>]'
      emptyMessage="""
        <input
          type='checkbox'
        />
        <$action-listops
          $tiddler='$:/ListedEditions'
          $field='text'
          $subfilter='+[append<currentTiddler>]'
        />"""
    >
      <input
        type='checkbox'
        checked
      />
      <$action-listops
        $tiddler='$:/ListedEditions'
        $field='text'
        $subfilter='+[remove<currentTiddler>]'
      />
    </$list>
    <$view
      tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
      field=title
    />
  </$button>
  <br/>
</$list>
